{"tid":1604971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線大問題 無武器係手","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:32:12.000Z","uid":220864,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"919dc4630112a5113e8e852163cd29c0f7d14e0b","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"為咗好好準備101<br />\n我地要吸取尋日嘅經驗<br />\n點解d畜龍一衝出嚟<br />\n就大量人淆底向後退?<br />\n我認為最大嘅問題係大部份人都係赤手空拳<br />\n我練過搏擊<br />\n深明如果單對單無武器係可以一戰<br />\n但係當對方有裝備加武器的時候<br />\n我地就變成低一級的武力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心理上絕對會受影響</span><br />\n<br />\n解決方法好簡單<br />\n姐係而家周街咁多地盤又搭竹棚<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家千奇唔好亂攞人地d竹</span><br />\n<br />\n我知你地個心理關口架<br />\n一定驚攞住架生就有位比人入<br />\n但係而家你咩都唔攞都比人打一鑊再拉48個鐘<br />\n再唔係黑警都塞野落你袋屈尻你<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5W5spVo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5W5spVo.jpg&h=1bb2d5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家提供建議<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ac226866e7df9dd61a3be7ba922a756fe66289bd","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f6d04158a3ff58e291d2e4c76d88b34eaec5626","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f1f057d4f4a87af2129bca5fedf8205b9b4b2ca","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75170f39c4dd357c0ad3ec7a7c2190a01b9623d9","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"650c1b4a34c960c9ed6169ae3c371102719848a8","tid":1604971,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb19297e4c0620d791fffd43056fd55d229e91bd","tid":1604971,"uid":262622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019